| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1383 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5e56e630-9ee6-51b4-90bc-87d8385445c2"
